#!/bin/bash
sudo dnf update -y
sudo dnf install -y postgresql15
sudo dnf install -y git docker
sudo systemctl start docker
sudo systemctl enable docker
sudo usermod -aG docker ec2-user
export AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=ap-northeast-1
cd /home/ec2-user
